Ultrabrain is an LCV-created local MCP reasoning gate for structured engineering
thought, validation, and review readiness.

No external model API is called by this package.

The MCP stdio entrypoint incorporates the audited, reachable subset of the
official `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` and its validation dependencies.
`dist/THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.txt`, generated during every package build,
contains their exact versions and complete license notices.
